OL,3,CVilla's Roman mosaic floor
OL,4,Cpainstakingly recreated over five years
OL,6,FThey spent the first two years hand-
OL,7,Fmaking the 140,000 stone and tile
OL,8,Fcubes (tesserae) using the same tools
OL,9,Fas the Romans.
OL,11,FOver the following three years they
OL,12,Frecreated a series of mosaic designs
OL,13,Fcopying ones from villas excavated in
OL,14,FSomerset - like Whatley, Hurcot,
OL,15,FNewton St Loe and Lopen, among others.
OL,17,FHow the cubes were made
