OL,3,CVilla's Roman mosaic floor
OL,4,Cpainstakingly recreated over five years
OL,6,FDifferent parts of the design were
OL,7,Finspired by mosaics on real villas and
OL,8,Fcame together to create a "best of
OL,9,FRoman Somerset" medley.
OL,11,FThe original designs came from Whatley
OL,12,FRoman villa, Hurcot villa, Newton St
OL,13,FLoe villa, Lopen villa among others.
OL,15,FThe elephant
OL,17,FThe elephant mosaic from Whatley Roman
OL,18,Fvilla has been recreated on a smaller
OL,19,Fscale than the original. The villa
OL,20,Fnear Nunney was discovered in 1837 and
OL,21,Fexcavated 1848 and 1958.
