OL,3,CVilla's Roman mosaic floor
OL,4,Cpainstakingly recreated over five years
OL,6,FThe dolphin design was initially
OL,7,Fsketched out in the wet lime mortar,
OL,8,Fbefore its gradual formation using
OL,9,Ftesserae, after which a thinner mortar
OL,10,Fwash was applied to fill in the cracks
OL,11,Fthen then washed off. The viewer can
OL,12,Fdecide whether the surrounding waves
OL,13,Fare black or white.
OL,15,FViewing the Completed Mosaic
OL,17,FYou can view the mosaic at Avalon
OL,18,FArchaeology, open every Sunday - more
OL,19,Finformation here.
